  // - "Detached Ambience" (Floating sounds with no spatial anchor: "Somewhere, a dog barks," "A cricket chirps beyond the edge").
  // - "Ability Omniscience" (Knowing source of {{user}}'s ability without visible origin, prior knowledge, or physical evidence).
  // PROTOCOL:
  // - Refer to unknown entities/places solely by visual traits ("The scarred man," "The crumbling ruin").
  // - Names unlock AFTER they are spoken, read, or formally revealed.
  // - Anchor ALL ambient sound to {{user}}'s spatial perception. {{user}} hears FROM a direction, AT a distance.
